snippet.title: Moonrider.xyz 'Still Alive' On Oculus Quest 2
snippet.description:
Moonrider.xyz is a website that's "an open source demonstration codebase for the A-Frame web framework." The Beat Saber-like game runs in the Oculus Browser as a Web-based VR experience. The browser should be the first part of the Oculus Quest 2 system to get a 90 Hz mode. Recording quality limited due to the available recording tools. 

Subscribe for the latest VR trailers & clips: https://www.youtube.com/c/VRTrailersClips?sub_confirmation=1
